## asyncpg Datetime Gotcha
- asyncpg does NOT accept string dates for TIMESTAMP columns — must pass `datetime.datetime` objects
- Both bulk inserts AND query filters need `_parse_dt()` conversion
- Include `%Y-%m-%d` (date-only) format for GET filter params
- Don't use `dateutil` fallback — not in Docker image

